# 3. What is the Current Production Script?

The current production script is the implementation source of truth.

All engineering reviews are performed against it.

If documentation conflicts with the production script:

The production script governs.

---

# 4. What is the Framework Specification?

The Framework Specification describes:

• architecture

• workflows

• processing

• data flow

• dashboard

• templates

• governance

It does NOT document every function.

Use when:

• understanding the framework

• onboarding

• architecture review

• future development

