# 20. Engineering Philosophy

The objective is continuous improvement of a stable production framework.

Preserve approved business rules.

Improve architecture.

Reduce complexity.

Maintain documentation.

Keep implementation and specifications synchronized.

The framework evolves through controlled engineering changes rather than complete rewrites.
